description: We are sisters with a rich background in professional cooking and hospitality. We also hold a national contract providing cooking services for NASCAR, Inc's elite cooking series, executives and VIP guests. We believe in using seasonal, simple ingredients to create new and classic recipes. We launched our food truck in January 2010. Since then, we have traveled, explored and enhanced our client dining experience in Northern California and greater bay area, and now we're bringing it to you on the streets!
name: The Grateful Gypsy Bistro
